4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course designed for beginners with no prior experience, aimed at preparing students for careers as data scientists. The course spans 16 weeks and includes Python, SQL, and statistics, focusing on building predictive models with popular libraries. Students will practice real-life cases and learn to strategize their AI projects through the entire lifecycle. Classes are held three times a week in small groups of 12, available in English or Spanish, and certificates are recognized by various organizations. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop